                        <span class="ml-4 font-medium text-lg">ビジネスマネージャーを作成した</span>
                    </label>
                    <label class="checklist-item flex items-center p-4 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-xl cursor-pointer transition-colors border border-white/10">
                        <input type="checkbox" class="w-6 h-6 rounded border-gray-300 text-meta focus:ring-meta bg-white cursor-pointer accent-green-500">
                        <span class="ml-4 font-medium text-lg">弊社をパートナーとして追加して「完了しました」と連絡した</span>
                    </label>
                    <label class="checklist-item flex items-center p-4 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-xl cursor-pointer transition-colors border border-white/10">
                        <input type="checkbox" class="w-6 h-6 rounded border-gray-300 text-meta focus:ring-meta bg-white cursor-pointer accent-green-500">
                        <span class="ml-4 font-medium text-lg">Facebookページをビジネスマネージャーに連携した</span>
                    </label>
                    <label class="checklist-item flex items-center p-4 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-xl cursor-pointer transition-colors border border-white/10">
                        <input type="checkbox" class="w-6 h-6 rounded border-gray-300 text-meta focus:ring-meta bg-white cursor-pointer accent-green-500">
                        <span class="ml-4 font-medium text-lg">Instagramアカウントを連携した</span>
                    </label>
                    <label class="checklist-item flex items-center p-4 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-xl cursor-pointer transition-colors border border-white/10">
                        <input type="checkbox" class="w-6 h-6 rounded border-gray-300 text-meta focus:ring-meta bg-white cursor-pointer accent-green-500">
                        <span class="ml-4 font-medium text-lg">クレジットカードを登録した</span>
                    </label>
                </div>

                <div id="completion-message" class="hidden transform transition-all duration-500 bg-white text-meta-dark p-6 rounded-xl text-center shadow-lg">
                    <i data-lucide="party-popper" class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto text-yellow-500 mb-3"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">お疲れ様でした！</h3>
                    <p class="font-medium">全部チェックできたら弊社に<strong>「設定完了しました！」</strong>と連絡してください。</p>
                    <p class="text-sm mt-2 text-gray-600">残りの作業（広告アカウントの作成・計測タグの設置など）は全て弊社側で行います。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Footer Help -->
        <div class="text-center pb-12">
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-2">何か分からないことがあれば、どのSTEPで詰まっているかを弊社にお伝えください。</p>
        </div>

    </main>

    <!-- Script for Checklist and Icons -->
    <script>
        // Initialize Lucide Icons
        lucide.createIcons();

        // Checklist Progress Logic
        const checkboxes = document.querySelectorAll('.checklist-item input[type="checkbox"]');
        const progressBar = document.getElementById('progress-bar');
        const progressText = document.getElementById('progress-text');
        const completionMessage = document.getElementById('completion-message');

        function updateProgress() {
            const total = checkboxes.length;
            const checked = document.querySelectorAll('.checklist-item input[type="checkbox"]:checked').length;
            const percentage = (checked / total) * 100;
            
            progressBar.style.width = `${percentage}%`;
            progressText.textContent = `${checked} / ${total} 完了`;
            
            // Visual feedback for checked items
            checkboxes.forEach(cb => {
                const parent = cb.closest('.checklist-item');
                if (cb.checked) {
                    parent.classList.add('opacity-50', 'bg-black/20');
                    parent.querySelector('span').classList.add('line-through');
                } else {
                    parent.classList.remove('opacity-50', 'bg-black/20');
                    parent.querySelector('span').classList.remove('line-through');
                }
            });

            if (percentage === 100) {
                completionMessage.classList.remove('hidden');
                // Optional: Scroll to completion message
                setTimeout(() => {
                    completionMessage.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' });
                }, 300);
            } else {
                completionMessage.classList.add('hidden');
            }
        }

        checkboxes.forEach(cb => {
            cb.addEventListener('change', updateProgress);
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
